---
title: Peach and Tomato Tart with Ricotta, Mint and Almonds
description: Elegant yet simple, this tart comes together in no time and makes you look like a pro! Honey, ricotta, tomatoes and peaches go together beautifully and taste indulgent with flaky puff pastry. A final flourish of mint and almonds finish this tart recipe with a bang!
